Offer description At Source Angel, our vibrant team, led by Danish management, upholds values of respect, people-centricity, and top-notch quality. Our culture emphasizes teamwork while still caring for the individual, elevating IT services, and helping global partners in optimizing development teams across Eastern Europe, supported by Scandinavian Management onsite. Join us to experience our deep commitment to our employees and discover numerous career opportunities. 
We are seeking a proficient Front-end Developer (Vue.js) to join a dynamic Danish startup specializing in crafting sophisticated customer management systems for physical casinos. The role involves crafting a web application primarily tailored for administrative web desktops, seamlessly integrating with multiple pre-existing casino systems. This innovative system stands as a bulwark against financial irregularities by providing comprehensive insights and robust reporting mechanisms concerning the casino's clientele. 

As part of our team, you’ll enjoy:  

Working in a small team directly with the decision maker;
Flexible working hours;
Hybrid model, 2-3 days from home/office;
20 days of paid vacation;
Paid National holidays;
Paid sick-leaves;
Health Insurence;
Corporate events.
